{
  "stem": "471.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I understood that, to steal a bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what a whole bread means?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She blinked me with her eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, blinked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I see, steal the bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was talking to the-- to the SS man who was watching us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, she makes him busy with a conversation or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took the bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that happen with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the only one-- one time I-- I had [? talked ?] [? honestly, ?] with her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I try-- when she was here last year, I try to remind her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She couldn't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She couldn't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which I don't blame her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I saw  him here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you know, he was saying that he remembers everybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But no, everybody remembers him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, let's don't fool our self.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He couldn't remember everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I remember the way he said goodbye to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That night, I remember they call a roll call, it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he had a little speech.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we could  hear, already, the-- the Russian Front approach closer, closer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You could see on the road, because this camp was a little bit-- on like, on a-- you know, like, in a canyon.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The SS army was running away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he came and he says, number one, he said to us-- this what I know of it, as an eyewitness.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, tomorrow-- what he said to the-- to the Germans, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm presuming only, this what they said in the pictures.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know how they said, in the pictures?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what actually happens, he came, he start to talk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, remember one thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
